  "notes": "Nouryon's personal care division offers a range of sustainable texture-modifying ingredients based on cellulose chemistry and biopolymers. Their Bermocoll™ cellulose ether range provides excellent thickening, film-forming, and texture-modifying performance across a wide range of pH values and formulation types. Nouryon's Amaze™ biopolymer film former is a sustainable, naturally derived alternative to synthetic film formers, delivering excellent hold and texture with a clean ingredient profile for eco-conscious brand formulations."
